New users can get Ethers from bank accounts.

(before purchasing a product)
Buyer/Seller/Agent buys BTK from MarketPlace.
Buyer/Seller/Agent approves MarketPlace to spend a certain amount of BTK. (same for selling BTK back to contract)

(when purchasing a product)
Same as the old MarketPlace sequence.

(before selling BTKs back to MarketPlace)
Buyer/Seller/Agent approves MarketPlace to spend a certain amount of BTK.

(to display all user balances on MarketPlace frontend)
Manually register all users you want to show on the page.

example: https://ethereum.org/en/developers/tutorials/transfers-and-approval-of-erc-20-tokens-from-a-solidity-smart-contract/
